					<div class="bio">
						<h4>Brendan Mac Evilly</h4>
												<button class="fa fa-link"></button>
												<p>Brendan Mac Evilly ’s writing has appeared in <i>The Irish Times, The Guardian, The Sunday Business Post, The Stinging Fly, The Honest Ulsterman,</i> and <i>We Are Dublin</i> among others. He works as a freelance arts manager and runs www.creativecareers.ie, a jobs website for the creative sector. His book <em>At Swim: A Book About the Sea</em> is published by Collins Press.</p>
